  voicePitch: 1
  dialogueLines:
  - '"Well well, I thought you''d mess it up."'
  - '"Turns out it was pretty decent."'
  - '"But decent doesn''t fix a bridge."'
  - '"What I need is a proper meal."'
  - '"Something with more substance, something hearty."'
  - '"Oh yes, I know."'
  - '"It needs different kind of vegetables."'
  - '"Bring me some pumpkin for this."'
  - '"There should be some pumpkin seeds in that beat up shed next to the farm."'
  - '"How''s the pumpkins going?"'
  - '"Ah yes much better. but..."'
